{
  "stem": "6277.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And sometimes they were worse than the German guards.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the first night we had beatings and killing again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we get stripped naked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They checked us for-- for lice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were shaved, taken to the showers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All this stuff was going on by screaming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was dark night, screaming, yelling, beating.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Taken to the shower, the shower, it was a fast enough shower, so it was the dripping the water, cold water was dripping.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they gave us some clothes, some [? lived-in ?] clothes, so they give us some clothes, whatever it was small or-- or-- or big.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took us to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the barracks they called it-- every barrack, it was called the block.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took us to the block.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The block has an elder, block elder.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The block elder was a kapo, one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Or he was from the German professional criminals, or there were Pole-- Poles, also criminals.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was empty yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The barrack was empty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had only straw sacks, sacks that was on this-- on the bare soil.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were sleeping there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in the morning they took us, chased us out for work in the camp the first morning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were shoveling there, straighten out the ground, working on the field there, on-- in the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was also working there, shoveling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they came, the administration of the camp, they were-- the commandant was [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Al-- ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Albert ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Sauer, ?] Obersturmfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he came and he-- he came and stopped where I was working.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he said to me-- screamed to me, he didn't talk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he said, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I'll show you how you have to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
